== 历史 ==
因在[[脱贫攻坚战|脱贫攻坚战]]中作出突出贡献，2021年2月25日[[全国脱贫攻坚总结表彰大会|全国脱贫攻坚总结表彰大会]]上，班玛县扶贫开发局被授予“全国脱贫攻坚先进集体”<ref>{{Cite web|title=关于全国脱贫攻坚先进个人先进集体拟表彰对象的公示|url=https://www.chinanews.com/gn/2021/02-10/9409480.shtml|accessdate=2021-03-12|work=[[中新网|中新网]]|archive-date=2021-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210215003222/http://www.chinanews.com/gn/2021/02-10/9409480.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=全国脱贫攻坚1981名先进个人和1501个先进集体名单发布|url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_11460123|accessdate=2021-03-12|work=[[澎湃新闻|澎湃新闻]]|archive-date=2021-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228125058/https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_11460123|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=全国脱贫攻坚先进个人1981名、先进集体1501个 名单公布|url=https://www.bjnews.com.cn/detail/161425514215596.html|accessdate=2021-03-12|work=[[北京新闻网|北京新闻网]]|archive-date=2021-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210820171915/https://www.bjnews.com.cn/detail/161425514215596.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=全国脱贫攻坚先进集体名单（1501个）|url=http://sn.people.com.cn/n2/2021/0226/c378287-34594296.html|accessdate=2021-03-12|work=[[人民网|人民网]]|archive-date=2021-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210719052429/http://sn.people.com.cn/n2/2021/0226/c378287-34594296.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

